description=Dawn Town was once known as a city that never truly slept. Its narrow streets are suffocated by layers of makeshift buildings, stacked so densely that the sky is barely visible. Endless prayers and constant arguments blend together day and night, like a ritual that never comes to an end. When disaster struck, the already fragile order collapsed almost instantly—gangs, cults, and survivor factions each claiming their own blocks. You won't find a true safe zone in Dawn Town, only corners that haven't been discovered yet.
